		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well it only works if my pot is turned from here to here. Otherwise one of the channels takes over. If my multimeter had batterys I'd measure.
<br />
<br />edit: btw I didnt use a 10k resistor but rather a 12k (had that laying round and couldnt find my 10k's) so for future reference in case you use the same resistor value as me.......might be a good idea to use 12k. (so the audio is evenly mixed if you use my values)
